(214, 'Problems', 'I have a problem, which is I’m getting better at everything related to my job since I started.', 163, 19, '2021-12-20 22:12:49', 0, NULL),
(215, 'Melons', 'Young players are like melons. Only when you open and taste the melon are you 100% sure that the melon is good.', 163, 19, '2021-12-20 22:13:14', 0, NULL),
(216, 'Justice', 'Soccer is not about justice. It’s a drama and criminally wrong decisions against you are part and parcel of that.', 174, 84, '2021-12-20 22:13:55', 0, NULL),
(217, 'Simple game', 'Football is a simple game; 22 men chase a ball for 90 minutes and at the end, the Germans win.', 37, 87, '2021-12-20 22:14:24', 0, NULL),
(218, 'Where are you?', 'My wife doesn’t like football. One day she called me ten minutes before a game to find out where I was.', 132, 18, '2021-12-20 22:14:48', 0, NULL),
(219, 'No excuses', 'I’d been ill and hardly trained for a week and I’d been out of the team for three weeks before that. So I wasn’t sharp. I got cramp before half-time as well. But I’m not one to make excuses.', 175, 50, '2021-12-20 22:15:33', 0, NULL),
(220, 'Not an iceberg', 'Apparently it’s my fault that the Titanic sank.', 176, 39, '2021-12-20 22:16:28', 0, NULL),
(221, 'Shocking Brazilians', 'The Brazilians were shocked, and I supposed that’s why they didn’t tackle me, because they thought there was no way an Englishman is going to do this.', 177, 84, '2021-12-20 22:17:05', 0, NULL),
(222, 'Tactics', 'Players lose you games, not tactics. There’s so much crap talk about tactics by people who barely know how to win at dominos.', 166, 68, '2021-12-20 22:17:28', 0, NULL),
(223, 'Pasta?', 'When an Italian tells me it’s pasta on the plate, I check under the sauce to make sure. They are the inventors of the smokescreen.', 22, 16, '2021-12-20 22:18:06', 0, NULL),
