(231, 'Noisy neighbours', 'Sometimes you have a noisy neighbour. You cannot do anything about that. They will always be noisy. You just have to get on with your life, put your television on, and turn it up a bit louder.', 22, 16, '2021-12-20 22:22:33', 0, NULL),
(232, 'Blackpool', 'I love Blackpool. We’re very similar. We both look better in the dark!', 176, 39, '2021-12-20 22:22:57', 0, NULL),
