(248, 'Just an analogy?', 'If you’re a burglar, it’s no good poncing about outside somebody’s house, looking good with your swag bad ready. Just get in there, burgle them and come out. I don’t advocate that obviously. It’s just an analogy.', 176, 39, '2021-12-20 22:33:40', 0, NULL),
