(251, 'Barnsley girls', 'The local girls are far uglier than the ones back in Belgrade or Skopje, the capital of Macedonia, where I come from. Our women are much prettier. Besides, they don’t drink as much beer as the Barnsley girls.', 184, 102, '2021-12-20 22:35:57', 0, NULL),
