(257, 'For the fish', 'The man who comes to take care of my piranhas told me that if I left West Ham he would kill all my fish.', 116, 20, '2022-01-03 11:48:03', 0, NULL),
(258, 'Belching and farting', 'Doping in English football is restricted to lager and baked beans with sausages. After which the players take to the field, belching and farting. English football culture is one of pure, intense competition, and that\'s why I have always preferred it to Italy.', 116, 20, '2022-01-03 11:49:19', 0, NULL),
(259, 'Transition', 'The shopping is not finished and before the pre-season starts I would like to bring in another two players. I like shopping, maybe I have become a woman.', 116, 20, '2022-01-03 11:49:54', 0, NULL),
